'''Ellie Farraday''' is a social worker who was sent to evaluated [[Cody|Cody's]] living situation.

==History==
Ellie was called in to evaluated [[Cody|Cody's]] living situation after Cooper became concerned about his mother's hoarding. She arrived at the house to find [[Andrea (Another Second Chance)|Andrea]] throwing things away and crying about what she'd lost. Violet said that they were making progress.

==Career==
She is a social worker for DCFS.
